---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import QuoteCTA from "../../components/QuoteCTA.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Plant Health Care (Tree & Shrub)"
  description="Plant health care for Central PA landscapes — insect, mite, and disease management for trees and shrubs, applied at the right time by a licensed applicator."
  path="/services/plant-health-care/"
>
  <section class="section pine-section">
    <div class="wrap"><p class="eyebrow">Service</p><h1>Plant Health Care</h1>
    <p class="lede">Keeping trees and shrubs healthy with the right input at the right moment.</p></div>
  </section>
  <section class="section"><div class="wrap prose">
    <h2>Trees and shrubs are an investment</h2>
    <p>Mature plantings add real value to a property and are expensive to replace. A plant health care program watches for insect, mite, and disease pressure and treats proactively — protecting the landscape and the pollinators that visit it.</p>
    <h2>What it covers</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Insect and mite management for ornamentals</li>
      <li>Disease monitoring and treatment</li>
      <li>Timing built around the plant's cycle, not the calendar</li>
    </ul>
    <!-- ✏️ EDIT: add the specific PHC inputs and equipment you use. -->
  </div></section>
  <QuoteCTA heading="Protect your trees and shrubs." />
</BaseLayout>
<style>.lede{font-size:1.2rem}.prose{max-width:46rem}.prose ul{padding-left:1.2rem}.prose li{margin-bottom:0.5rem}</style>
